       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID. REFADJ2.
      * REFUND ADJUSTMENT - CUTOFF CONSTANTS FROM WSCUTOFF COPYBOOK
       ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
       DATA DIVISION.
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
       COPY WSCUTOFF.
       01  WS-CREDIT-LIMIT           PIC 9(9)V99 VALUE ZERO.
       01  WS-REFUND-AMT             PIC 9(7)V99 VALUE ZERO.
       01  WS-CUTOFF                 PIC 9(7)V99 VALUE ZERO.
       01  WS-ACTION                 PIC X(8) VALUE SPACES.
       PROCEDURE DIVISION.
       1000-MAIN.
           ACCEPT WS-CREDIT-LIMIT
           ACCEPT WS-REFUND-AMT
           PERFORM 2000-CUTOFF
           DISPLAY 'ACTION: ' WS-ACTION
           STOP RUN.
       2000-CUTOFF.
           COMPUTE WS-CUTOFF = WS-CREDIT-LIMIT * WS-CUTOFF-PCT
           IF WS-CUTOFF > WS-CUTOFF-CAP
              MOVE WS-CUTOFF-CAP TO WS-CUTOFF
           END-IF
           IF WS-REFUND-AMT > WS-CUTOFF
              MOVE 'CONSENT' TO WS-ACTION
           ELSE
              MOVE 'ADJUST' TO WS-ACTION
           END-IF.
